<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Patch>
  <Operation Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
    <mods>
      <li>Hospitality: Vending machines</li>
    </mods>
    <match Class="PatchOperationSequence">
      <success>Always</success>
      <operations>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="MedievalVendingMachine"]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>자판기 선반</label>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="MedievalVendingMachine"]/description</xpath>
          <value>
            <description>간단하게 손님에게 물건을 팔 수 있습니다. 대규모 판매 구역을 설정하거나 자동 판매기를 만들고 싶지 않은 경우 최적의 선택입니다.</description>
          </value>
        </li>
      </operations>
    </match>
  </Operation>
  <Operation Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
    <mods>
      <li>Cash Register</li>
    </mods>
    <match Class="PatchOperationSequence">
      <success>Always</success>
      <operations>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="CashRegister_CashRegister"]/description</xpath>
          <value>
            <description>음식점과 상점을 관리할 수 있는 금전 등록기입니다.</description>
          </value>
        </li>
      </operations>
    </match>
  </Operation>
  <Operation Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
    <mods>
      <li>Hospitality: Spa</li>
    </mods>
    <match Class="PatchOperationSequence">
      <success>Always</success>
      <operations>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="DBHSaunaHeaterElec"]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>전기 사우나 난방기</label>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="DBHSaunaHeaterLog"]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>화력발전 사우나 난방기</label>
          </value>
        </li>
        <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
          <success>Always</success>
          <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="DBHSaunaSeating"]/label</xpath>
          <value>
            <label>사우나 좌석</label>
          </value>
        </li>
      </operations>
    </match>
  </Operation>
</Patch>